{
  "stem": "8947.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I have to tell me about-- about our system, our school system, before you and I can mention that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- in our school system, we had four elementary schools.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had eight gymnasiums.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, the gymnasium incorporated really four years of college.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because at the end of your fourth years of gymnasium, you had to decide what profession you are going to select.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you wanted to go to medical school, then you had to take sciences.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if you wanted to go to literature, naturally you have to take arts, arts classes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so I had the four elementary schools.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had my eight gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then after the eight gymnasium, you have a very strict exam, called Baccalaureate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you have to master all the subjects that you had through the eight years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's the nightmare of everyone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it's a big test, which can last several days, and oral and written for every subject.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, after you get-- you-- you pass this test-- you have to pass this test-- then you get the Bachelor of Science or Bachelor of Art degree.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And now, if you wanted to go to the university-- suppose you wanted to be an engineer or you wanted to go into arts, you didn't need anything else except this and you automatically registered.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If you wanted to go to medical school, which was my dream, you couldn't.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because you have to pass an entrance examination, you know, to the medical school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I-- I got the entrance examination.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I continued my studies after I came back from the camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I have-- I was in my second year of medical school when we emigrated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was my dream, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
